Requires tasmota-display.bin

Configure display:

```
Backlog DisplayModel 2; DisplayCols 21; DisplayRows 8; DisplayMode 2;
```

Push the "BOOT" button to enable the display. You can also use the "Toggle" button in the Tasmota web interface.